data.description: MOTIVATED SELLERS!! Welcome home to this beautiful 1 story, corner home in pristine condition located in Master-planned community of Balmoral located in Humble, Texas. Convenient with beautiful lagoon, walking trails and partake in the many activities and amenities that in the neighborhood.  The beautiful open concept in this home is wonderful! You can enjoy family time as you cook and or even entertain. In the kitchen, you will be presented with ample counter space, cabinet space and stainless-steel appliances. This home is a true must see!! Schedule your private showing today!
